<div class="section" id="frequently-asked-questions">
<span id="faq"></span><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
<dl class="docutils">
<dt>What happened to the comments?</dt>
<dd>I've converted all of the answers found in the old comments into
FAQs just like this on every excercise.  The comments started being
nothing but me checking people's homework rather than help with the
exercises, so I felt rolling the important responses into well written
FAQs was better for everyone.</dd>
<dt>Can I buy the PDF by itself?</dt>
<dd>No, I'm trying to simplify everything I make now so I can produce more
books rather than manage a ton of sales.  I'm now simply bundling the
PDF and Videos together and setting the price so they are still a great
value.</dd>
<dt>Can I email you to get help?</dt>
<dd>Sure. Email <a class="reference external" href="mailto:help&#64;learncodethehardway.org">help&#64;learncodethehardway.org</a> and I'll try to help when I
can.  I'm usually very fast with my responses, but if I don't reply
I may have just deleted your email on accident thinking it's spam.
Email me again if that happens.</dd>
</dl>
